name: Malaventura's Tauromaquia 03
description: Tauromaquia has its roots in the minoan civilization and there are many artistic representations about it since then. From the classics to Goya or Picasso, the bullfighting has always operate an strange attraction to the eye. This furious martyrdom of the bull and its symbolic meaning traveled for centuries until this series where malaventura explore the movement and typical scenes on the "plaza" but glitching the tradition transforming everything into a pixel dance where the bull lives forever
